        "translations": {
          "en": "Muhammad ibn al-Hasan ibn Ahmad ibn al-Walid (may God be pleased with him) narrated to us. He said: Muhammad ibn al-Hasan al-Saffar narrated to us, from al-Abbas ibn Ma'ruf, from Bakr ibn Muhammad al-Azdi, from Abu Basir. He said: Abu Abdillah al-Sadiq (peace be upon him) said:",
